研究了当前 NSCLC 治疗对肠道菌群和代谢的影响，探讨了微生物组与治疗反应之间的关系，并强调了益生菌、微生物代谢物、粪便菌群移植（FMT）和饮食干预在 NSCLC 管理中的关键作用。通过阐明肠道微生物群及其代谢物调节治疗功效的机制，我们研究了针对肠道生态系统的外源干预措施在增强治疗效果和减轻不良反应方面的潜力。调节肠道微生物群代表了一种有前景的临床途径，并为未来非小细胞肺癌治疗策略的发展提供了新的前沿。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/immunomodulatory-role-of-microbiota-in-inflammation-and-cancer.webp" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Nov 2025 12:00:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2025/11/immunomodulatory-role-of-microbiota-in-inflammation-and-cancer</guid></item><item><title>光速人工智能刚刚成为可能</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2025/11/ai-at-the-speed-of-light-just-became-a-possibility</link><description>阿尔托大学的研究人员展示了光速下的单次张量计算，这是迈向由光学计算而不是电子技术驱动的下一代通用人工智能硬件的显着一步。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/ai-at-the-speed-of-light-just-became-a-possibility.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Nov 2025 11:45:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2025/11/ai-at-the-speed-of-light-just-became-a-possibility</guid></item><item><title>中国科学家发现月球铁锈，揭示月球新氧化过程</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2025/11/chinese-scientists-discover-lunar-rust-revealing-new-oxidation-process-on-the-moon</link><description>中国科学家首次在嫦娥六号任务从月球背面带回的月球土壤样本中鉴定出微米级的赤铁矿和磁赤铁矿晶体。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/chinese-scientists-discover-lunar-rust-revealing-new-oxidation-process-on-the-moon.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Nov 2025 11:30:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2025/11/chinese-scientists-discover-lunar-rust-revealing-new-oxidation-process-on-the-moon</guid></item><item><title>人工智能泡泡</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2025/11/ai-bubble</link><description>很多人都在谈论人工智能泡沫，因为技术在一段时间内爆炸式增长，然后稍微崩溃，然后最终再次向前发展，这是正常的。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/images/ai.bubble.webp" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Nov 2025 11:15:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2025/11/ai-bubble</guid></item><item><title>记忆在对个人有意义的音乐中跨越生命周期</titl